article.description: — Jarred Godfrey had 21 points as Purdue Fort Wayne defeated IUPUI 72-57 on Thursday night.
article.headline: Godfrey carries Purdue Fort Wayne over IUPUI 72-57
article.linkText: Godfrey carries Purdue Fort Wayne over IUPUI 72-57
article.story: FORT WAYNE, Ind. -- — Jarred Godfrey had 21 points as Purdue Fort Wayne defeated IUPUI 72-57 on Thursday night. Jalon Pipkins had 13 points and seven rebounds for Purdue Fort Wayne (14-10, 9-6 Horizon League), which earned its sixth straight home victory. Deonte Billups added 12 points. B.J. Maxwell had 19 points for the Jaguars (2-20, 0-11). Nathan McClure added 17 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
